data.description: Ideal location on a corner lot and inground, heated pool with screen enclosure awaits. This lovely 1 story, 3 bedroom, brick home features 3 full bathrooms. Is not in a flood zone and no HOA. Renovations include a large, heated and cooled Florida room overlooking the pool. Plus an updated kitchen complete with granite counters, island, stainless steel appliances and range hood. Electric and natural gas options for maximized energy efficiency. Prelisting home inspection provided and repairs deemed necessary will be completed. A new roof and water heater will be installed and home warranty included for peace of mind. Survey available and Seller to assist with closing costs. Welcome to your new home with option of short or long term rental. More photos to come.
